data.description: Gov Willis Home- Big & Beautiful Victorian in Desirable Historic Northwest Delaware! Relax on One of Three Porches. Inviting Entry w/ Fireplace, Dramatic Staircase & Stained Glass Window. Dining Room has Easy Access to Butler Pantry & Powder Room. Spacious Family Room. Living Room w/ Fireplace Overlooks Covered Front Porch. Marble Flooring in Kitchen along with Solid Wood Cabinets, Coffee Bar & Deck Access.  Upstairs find the Opulent Owner Suite w/ Bay Window & Private Porch, Incredibly Updated Hall Bath, 3rd Bedroom ( Seller used as an Office) & Guest Room w/Private Full Bath. Huge 3rd Floor Suite w/ Full Bath & Cozy Covered Porch, Exposed Brick Accent. Fresh Paint, Brand New Tankless H2O & Water Line. Windows & HVAC New in 2018, Fridge, Stove & D/W New in 2020. Own A Piece of History!
